fields.value: Supplementary Information, Flowers visitors of the licuri palm (Syagrus coronata): brood pollinators in a diverse community of antagonists and mutualists

dsDescriptionValue.value: This dataset includes Supplementary Files showing details of the behavior of flower visitors of Syagrus coronata. See the main article for more information: de Medeiros BAS et al. 2019. Flowers visitors of the licuri palm (Syagrus coronata): brood pollinators in a diverse community of antagonists and mutualists. Biological Journal of the Linnean Society. doi:10.1093/biolinnean/blz008

publicationCitation.value: de Medeiros BAS, Núñez-Avellaneda LA, Hernandez AM, Farrell BD. 2019. Flowers visitors of the licuri palm (Syagrus coronata): brood pollinators in a diverse community of antagonists and mutualists. Biological Journal of the Linnean Society.
